file.name: twilio_flex_v1.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    test_enum_status:
      enum:
        - in-progress
        - paused
        - stopped
        - processing
        - completed
        - absent
      type: string
    test.response_object:
      properties:
        account_sid:
          nullable: true
          format: foobar
          type: string
        sid:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        test_string:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        test_integer:
          nullable: true
          type: integer
      type: object
  examples:
    test.response_object.example:
      value:
        sid: "CR12345678123456781234567812345678"
        test_string: "Ahoy"
  securitySchemes:
    accountSid_authToken:
      scheme: basic
      type: http
info:
  contact:
    email: support@twilio.com
    name: Twilio Support
    url: https://support.twilio.com
  description: This is the public Twilio REST API.
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
  termsOfService: https://www.twilio.com/legal/tos
  title: Twilio - Accounts
  version: 1.11.0
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /v1/Credentials:
    description: A parent resource with no operations
    servers:
      - url: https://flex-api.twilio.com
    x-twilio:
      pathType: list
  /v1/Credentials/AWS:
    get:
      operationId: ListCredentialAws
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: PageSize
          schema:
            maximum: 1000
            minimum: 1
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  credentials:
                    items:
                      $ref: '#/components/schemas/test.response_object'
                    type: array
                  meta:
                    properties:
                      first_page_url:
                        format: uri
                        type: string
                      key:
                        type: string
                      next_page_url:
                        format: uri
                        type: string
                      page:
                        type: integer
                      page_size:
                        type: integer
                      previous_page_url:
                        format: uri
                        type: string
                      url:
                        format: uri
                        type: string
                    type: object
                title: ListCredentialAwsResponse
                type: object
              examples:
                creds_response_example:
                  summary: Example of a Credential
                  value:
                    credentials: [
                      {
                        "account_sid": "AC12345678123456781234567812345678",
                        "sid": "CR12345678123456781234567812345678",
                        "test_string": "Ahoy",
                      }
                    ]
                    meta: {
                      first_page_url: "http://example.com/page1",
                      next_page_url: "http://example.com/page2",
                      page: 1,
                      page_size: 3,
                      previous_page_url: "http://example.com/page0",
                      url: "http://example.com"
                    }
          description: OK
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    post:
      operationId: CreateCredentialAws
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              properties:
                TestString:
                  type: string
                TestBoolean:
                  type: boolean
                TestInteger:
                  type: integer
                TestNumber:
                  type: number
                TestNumberFloat:
                  type: number
                  format: float
                TestNumberDouble:
                  type: number
                  format: double
                TestNumberInt32:
                  type: number
                  format: int32
                TestNumberInt64:
                  type: integer
                  format: int64
                TestObject:
                  type: object
                  format: object
                TestDateTime:
                  type: string
                  format: date-time
                TestDate:
                  type: string
                  format: date
                TestEnum:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/test_enum_status'
                  type: string
                TestObjectArray:
                  items:
                    type: object
                  type: array
                TestAnyType: { }
                TestAnyArray:
                  items: {}
                  type: array
                Permissions:
                  description: 'A comma-separated list of the permissions you will
                                      request from the users of this ConnectApp.  Can include: `get-all`
                                      and `post-all`.'
                  items:
                    enum:
                      - get-all
                      - post-all
                    type: string
                  type: array
                SomeA2PThing:
                  type: string
              required:
                - TestString
              title: CreateCredentialAwsRequest
              type: object
      responses:
        '201':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/test.response_object'
          description: Created
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
      x-twilio:
        className: new_credentials
        mountName: new_credentials
        conditional:
          - - TestInteger
            - TestDate
          - - TestNumberFloat
            - TestObject
    servers:
      - url: https://flex-api.twilio.com
    x-twilio:
      parent: /Credentials
      pathType: list
  /v1/Credentials/AWS/{Sid}:
    delete:
      operationId: DeleteCredentialAws
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: Sid
          required: true
          schema:
            maxLength: 34
            minLength: 34
            pattern: ^CR[0-9a-fA-F]{32}$
            type: string
      responses:
        '204':
          description: The resource was deleted successfully.
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    get:
      operationId: FetchCredentialAws
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: Sid
          required: true
          schema:
            maxLength: 34
            minLength: 34
            pattern: ^CR[0-9a-fA-F]{32}$
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/test.response_object'
              examples:
                example:
                  $ref: '#/components/examples/test.response_object.example'
          description: OK
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    post:
      operationId: UpdateCredentialAws
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: Sid
          required: true
          schema:
            maxLength: 34
            minLength: 34
            pattern: ^CR[0-9a-fA-F]{32}$
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              properties:
                TestString:
                  type: string
                TestBoolean:
                  type: boolean
              title: UpdateCredentialAwsRequest
              type: object
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/test.response_object'
          description: OK
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    servers:
      - url: https://flex-api.twilio.com
    x-twilio:
      parent: /Credentials
      pathType: instance
  /v1/Credentials/AWS/{Sid}/History:
    description: A nested instance resource under an instance resource
    get:
      operationId: FetchCredentialHistory
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: Sid
          required: true
          schema:
            maxLength: 34
            minLength: 34
            pattern: ^CR[0-9a-fA-F]{32}$
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: AddOnsData
          schema:
            type: object
            format: prefixed-collapsible-map-AddOns
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/test.response_object'
          description: OK
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    servers:
      - url: https://flex-api.twilio.com
    x-twilio:
      parent: /Credentials/AWS/{Sid}
      pathType: instance
  /v1/Voice/{Sid}:
    description: An instance resource with no parent
    post:
      operationId: UpdateCall
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: Sid
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  sid:
                    nullable: true
                    type: string
                type: object
          description: OK
      security:
        - accountSid_authToken: [ ]
    servers:
      - url: https://flex-api.twilio.com
    x-twilio:
      pathType: instance
      mountName: calls
